1
00:00:01,640 --> 00:00:02,880
Sigh.

2
00:00:03,640 --> 00:00:05,680
Living together is really something else.

3
00:00:06,880 --> 00:00:07,880
Huh?

4
00:00:08,840 --> 00:00:10,080
Did you get some rest?

5
00:00:10,840 --> 00:00:13,360
Sorry, just give me a second.

6
00:00:13,360 --> 00:00:15,720
Wait, wait, wait. Don't go to all that trouble.

7
00:00:16,120 --> 00:00:18,520
Let's just grab something from the convenience store or order takeout.

8
00:00:18,520 --> 00:00:19,720
Iijima Hinata.

9
00:00:23,680 --> 00:00:26,200
Just a drop more olive oil.

10
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:34,920
There, all done!

11
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:37,000
Mmm!

12
00:00:42,280 --> 00:00:43,840
This is amazing!

13
00:00:43,840 --> 00:00:45,640
I had no idea you were such a good cook.

14
00:00:46,000 --> 00:00:48,280
I've been cooking for myself since I was a kid.

15
00:00:49,360 --> 00:00:50,560
Since my mom passed away.

16
00:00:52,480 --> 00:00:53,920
My dad...

17
00:00:53,920 --> 00:00:56,440
He's truly happy to have married your mom.

18
00:00:58,000 --> 00:01:00,360
To make sure they feel like remarrying was the right choice,

19
00:01:01,080 --> 00:01:02,840
we should try to get along well, too.

20
00:01:03,600 --> 00:01:05,280
You're right!

21
00:01:08,480 --> 00:01:09,600
This dish...

22
00:01:10,200 --> 00:01:12,760
It's the first time I've made it for anyone else.

23
00:01:14,800 --> 00:01:16,120
In that case,

24
00:01:16,120 --> 00:01:18,080
I'll make sure to tell you how delicious it is every single day.

25
00:01:21,520 --> 00:01:24,040
The way you say that...

26
00:01:25,360 --> 00:01:27,080
- Are you proposing to me?
- You're such a dork.
